    "content": "# Getting Started with Badget\n\nWelcome to Badget! This guide will help you get up and running with our link management platform in just a few minutes.\n\n## What is Badget?\n\nBadget is a powerful link management platform that helps you create, track, and optimize your links. Whether you're a marketer, developer, or content creator, Badget provides the tools you need to manage your links effectively.\n\n## Creating Your Account\n\n1. **Sign Up**: Visit [badget.app](https://badget.app) and click \"Sign Up\"\n2. **Verify Email**: Check your email and click the verification link\n3. **Complete Setup**: Add your basic information and preferences\n\n## Creating Your First Link\n\n### Using the Dashboard\n\n1. Click the **\"Create Link\"** button on your dashboard\n2. Enter your destination URL\n3. Customize your short link (optional)\n4. Add tags and description for organization\n5. Click **\"Create\"** to generate your short link\n\n### Using the API\n\nFor developers, you can create links programmatically:\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://api.badget.app/links \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"url\": \"https://example.com\",\n    \"alias\": \"my-first-link\"\n  }'\n```\n\n## Understanding Analytics\n\nOnce you've created links, you can track their performance:\n\n- **Click Counts**: See how many times your links have been clicked\n- **Geographic Data**: Understand where your audience is located\n- **Referrer Sources**: Know where your traffic is coming from\n- **Device Information**: Learn about your audience's devices\n\n## Best Practices\n\n### Link Organization\n\n- **Use Tags**: Organize your links with relevant tags\n- **Descriptive Aliases**: Create memorable, branded short links\n- **Consistent Naming**: Develop a naming convention for your team\n\n### Security\n\n- **Custom Domains**: Use your own domain for better brand trust\n- **Access Control**: Manage team permissions appropriately\n- **Regular Reviews**: Audit your links periodically\n\n## Quick Tips\n\n1. **Bulk Operations**: Use our bulk import feature for multiple links\n2. **QR Codes**: Generate QR codes for offline campaigns\n3. **Expiration Dates**: Set expiration dates for time-sensitive campaigns\n4. **UTM Parameters**: Add tracking parameters automatically\n\n## Need Help?\n\n- **Documentation**: Browse our comprehensive [help center](/help)\n- **API Reference**: Check out our [API documentation](/help/api-reference)\n- **Support**: Contact our team at support@badget.app\n- **Community**: Join our Discord for community support\n\n## Next Steps\n\nNow that you've created your first link, explore these advanced features:\n\n- [Set up custom domains](/help/custom-domains) for branded links\n- [Learn about our API](/help/api-reference) for integrations\n- [Understand analytics](/help/analytics) to optimize your campaigns\n\nReady to get started? [Create your first link](https://app.badget.app) today!",
